* [[At least 100]]% of [[mediacrat]]'s [[sex]]ual partners now have [[herpes]].
* [[Quasidan's penis]] has caused [[vagina]]l bleeding due to its enormous size in 60% of the [[women]] it has [[fuck]]ed.
